This is a practical, affordable version of the Omni-Lattice metamaterial cloak that can be built in a well-equipped makerspace using off-the-shelf tools and low-cost micro-optics.

### ðŸ”§ Core Components
- **3D-printed micro-cell lattice** (resin SLA printer for precision)
- **Flexible optical panels** using lenticular + Fresnel hybrid layering
